.slider{
	white-space: nowrap;
	overflow: auto;
	overflow-y: hidden;
	height: 300px;
}

.slider .slide{
	margin: 10px;
	white-space: normal;
	display: inline-block;
}

.slider .slider-header{
	margin-left: 10px;
	font-weight: bold;
}
.slide-wrapper .slide-image{
	width: 300px;
	height: 300px;
}

.slide-wrapper .slide-image img{
	width: 100%;
	height: auto;
}

.slide-wrapper .slide-text{
	color: white;
	top: -300px;
	left: 10px;
	position: relative;
	text-shadow: black 3px 3px 3px;
}
